@using Bonsai.Code.DomainModel.Facts.Models
@using Bonsai.Code.Services
@using Bonsai.Localization
@using Impworks.Utils.Format
<script type="text/x-template" data-kind="fact-template" id="LanguageFactModel">
    <div class="fact-wrapper">
        <h6>
            {{def.title}}
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" v-on:click="add({}, 'language')" title="@Texts.Admin_Pages_Facts_Add">
                <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
            </button>
        </h6>
        <div v-if="!emptyList()" class="fact-list">
            <div class="row" v-for="row in getList()">
                <div class="col-sm-8 form form-fact fact-list-item">
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group col-sm-8">
                            <label>@Texts.Admin_Pages_Facts_Language</label>
                            <input type="text" v-model="row.Name" class="form-control form-control-sm mr-2" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-sm-4">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-sm btn-remove-fact" v-on:click="remove(row)" title="@Texts.Admin_Pages_Facts_Remove">
                                <i class="fa fa-remove"></i>
                            </button>
                            <label>@Texts.Admin_Pages_Facts_LanguageLevel</label>
                            <select v-model="row.Proficiency" class="form-control form-control-sm mr-2">
                                <option v-bind:value="null">@Texts.Admin_Pages_Facts_Unspecified</option>
                                @foreach(var prof in LocaleProvider.GetLocaleEnumDescriptions<LanguageProficiency>())
                                {
                                    <option value="@prof.Key">@prof.Value</option>
                                }
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <duration-picker v-model="row.Duration" size="sm" margin="2" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</script>